  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Entity, Item, Tile

    public abstract class LevelObject
extends com.badlogic.gdx.graphics.g2d.Sprite
    A LevelObject class which is a Super class to all tile and item objects. It includes variables and methods familiar in the aforementioned objects

        Constructor method for instancing a level object. This sets the dimension, locations and has objects to observe collisions
        Parameters:
        x - x-axis co-ordinate of object
        y - y-axis co-ordinate of object
        name - name of the object
        img - Texture of the image
        textureAtlas - is the Atlas where the images are derived from
